Titolo: Conflict: Global Terror

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Conflict: Global Terror (also called Conflict: Global Storm) is a tactical shooter video game developed by Pivotal Games and Synergenix, and published by SCi Games and 2K Games for PlayStation 2, Xbox and Microsoft Windows. It is the fourth installment in the Conflict series.
The action focuses on an elite rapid response special forces unit, using the four original members of the Desert Storm series and a new member. Bradley, Foley, Connors, Jones and Sherman must overcome terrorists over many different countries, including Colombia, South Korea, Ukraine, Egypt, the Philippines and Kashmir.